Package: embeddcv
Title: Embeddings and Cosine Similarity Analysis for Psychological Scales
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "Primi", , "ricprimi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analyzing psychological scales using embeddings and cosine similarity.
    The package provides functions to generate embeddings from text using OpenAI's API,
    compute cosine similarities between items and scales, and analyze the relationships
    between items and factors using various complexity measures.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
